init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The first was a car accident on New Year's Eve of 2002.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was the only one in the car when it crashed.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was kept captive by fans, who wanted to keep him because he was famous.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is the only one who can save us from the evil's of the universe.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This team includes an Army General, two scientists, a psychic woman who can locate him by using time travel.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The people are happy that their hero is back.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matt Damon is happy to be home.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He gets a huge hero's welcome.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But he is still pretty shaken up by the whole experience.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But the government says he has to keep it a secret.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matt Damon is upset about this.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He goes to the psychic woman and tells her everything he knows about the aliens.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The next day she is on a talk show and she tells the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The people take to the streets and protest.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was the greatest president to ever live.
